Package org.openbel.framework.core.protocol.handler

BEL protocol handlers and implementation utilities.

See:
          Description

Interface Summary
ProtocolHandler ProtocolHandler defines an object that understands how to read data from a protocol.
 

Class Summary
AbstractHttpProtocolHandler AbstractHttpProtocolHandler provides boiler-plate IO to read from an HttpURLConnection and write to a File.
AbstractProtocolHandler AbstractProtocolHandler provides boiler-plate IO to read from a InputStream and write to a File.
FileProtocolHandler FileProtocolHandler implements an AbstractProtocolHandler to download a resource from a file:// url.
FTPConnector FTPConnector implements the ftp client connector which is responsible for: authenticating with the ftp server retrieves a file from the connected ftp server
FTPProtocolHandler FileProtocolHandler implements an ProtocolHandler to download a resource from a ftp:// url.
HttpProtocolHandler HttpProtocolHandler implements an AbstractHttpProtocolHandler to download a resource from an http:// url.
HttpsProtocolHandler HttpsProtocolHandler implements an AbstractHttpProtocolHandler to download a resource from an https:// secure url.
SftpProtocolHandler SftpProtocolHandler implements a ProtocolHandler that can read from a sftp url.
 

Enum Summary
SupportedProtocol SupportedProtocol defines the url schemes supported by the OpenBEL Framework.
 

Package org.openbel.framework.core.protocol.handler Description
